#org @gText_UteyanRuins_BrailleMan
Until recently, an old man was\nstudying the ruins day and night.\pHe was certain the symbols on the\nruins could be deciphered.\pLast I heard, he went home to\nLaplaz Town to finish his work.\pI wonder how he's doing these days?

#org @gText_UteyanRuins_BrailleMan_WithDecoder
Oh! That device!\pThat's the one the old man was\nworking on.\pSo the old coot managed to get it\nworking after all, huh?

#org @gText_UteyanRuins_PuzzleGirl
I think I see a pattern in some\nof the symbols on the ruins.\pI wonder if the symbols are actually\ntrying to spell out words?\pHmm[.] I need to think about it some\nmore.

